---
---

<section id="servizi" class="py-20 bg-zinc-950">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-14">
      <p class="text-brand text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-3">Cosa facciamo</p>
      <h2 class="text-white text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-black mb-4">I nostri servizi</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-400 max-w-xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        Ci occupiamo di tutto: dalla pianificazione al montaggio finale. Scegli il servizio
        di cui hai bisogno, pensiamo noi al resto.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-14">
      <div class="border border-white/10 hover:border-brand/50 rounded-2xl p-8 group transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brand/10 group-hover:bg-brand rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 transition-colors duration-300">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-brand group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M3 9l9-7 9 7v11a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2z"></path>
            <polyline points="9 22 9 12 15 12 15 22"></polyline>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-white text-xl font-bold mb-3">Traslochi Residenziali</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed text-sm">
          Ti accompagniamo nel trasferimento della tua casa, con cura per ogni dettaglio:
          imballaggio professionale, trasporto sicuro, montaggio mobili nella nuova abitazione.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="border border-white/10 hover:border-brand/50 rounded-2xl p-8 group transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brand/10 group-hover:bg-brand rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 transition-colors duration-300">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-brand group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300" aria-hidden="true">
            <rect x="2" y="7" width="20" height="14" rx="2" ry="2"></rect>
            <path d="M16 21V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-white text-xl font-bold mb-3">Traslochi Aziendali</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed text-sm">
          Spostiamo uffici, attività commerciali e magazzini minimizzando i tempi di fermo.
          Lavoriamo anche nel weekend per non interrompere la tua attività.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="border border-white/10 hover:border-brand/50 rounded-2xl p-8 group transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brand/10 group-hover:bg-brand rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 transition-colors duration-300">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-brand group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M14.7 6.3a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.4l1.6 1.6a1 1 0 0 0 1.4 0l3.77-3.77a6 6 0 0 1-7.94 7.94l-6.91 6.91a2.12 2.12 0 0 1-3-3l6.91-6.91a6 6 0 0 1 7.94-7.94l-3.76 3.76z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-white text-xl font-bold mb-3">Montaggio Mobili</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed text-sm">
          Smontaggio e rimontaggio preciso di qualsiasi tipo di mobile: armadi, librerie,
          cucine, letti. Anche senza trasloco, se ne hai bisogno.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center">
      <a
        href="/servizi"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-brand hover:bg-brand-dark text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-bold transition-colors duration-200"
      >
        Scopri tutti i servizi →
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
